<LP>
   PARIS -- Airbus Industrie said Mexicana de Aviacion signed
a contract to buy 22 of the European aircraft consortium's
A-320 commercial jets and take options on an additional 14
planes, firming up a commitment that was announced in May.
   Financial details of the order weren't disclosed, but
people in the industry estimate the price of one Airbus A-320
