   BIOCRAFT LABORATORIES Inc. (Fair Lawn, N.J.) -- Steven J.
Sklar, who is currently vice president and treasurer, was
named to the additional post of chief financial officer of
this maker of generic pharmaceutical products. Biocraft also
named three new vice presidents: Beryl Snyder, 33, currently
general counselor; Brian Snyder, 32, currently controller;
and Jay Snyder, 32, currently director of research and
product development.
