<LP>
   The following were among yesterday's offerings and
pricings in U.S. and non-U.S. capital markets, with terms and
syndicate manager, as compiled by Dow Jones Capital Markets
Report.
                                                                                                       

                          MUNICIPAL
                                                                                                       

</LP>
<TEXT>
   Maricopa County, Ariz. -- $75 million of Series 1990C
general obligation bonds, via a Marine Midland Capital
Markets Corp. group. The bonds, rated double-A-1/double-A,
were priced for reoffering to yield from 6.65% in 1999 to
